The paper deals with the study of the local structure of finite algebras, which is a topic in mathematical logic and algebra. Therefore, cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses graph-like structures and connectivity properties, which are topics in discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The study of term operations and their behavior is related to the study of algorithms and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the mention of the Constraint Satisfaction Problem suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
